ctypes: ctypes (ffi package for Python)
ctypes: 
ctypes: ctypes is a ffi (Foreign Function Interface) package for Python.
ctypes: 
ctypes: It allows to call functions exposed from dlls/shared libraries
ctypes: and has extensive facilities to create, access and manipulate
ctypes: simpole and complicated C data types transparently from Python -
ctypes: in other words: wrap libraries in pure Python.
